          <a:p>
            <a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750" algn="ctr">
              <a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/>
              <a:buChar char="•"/>
            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>Target Audience: Indian urban police forces, municipal emergency services, traffic management authorities</a:t>
            </a:r>
          </a:p>
          <a:p>
            <a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750" algn="ctr">
              <a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/>
              <a:buChar char="•"/>
            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>Social Impact: Reduces fatal accident response from 16+ min to under 2.5 min. Estimated 50,000+ lives saved/year if deployed across India&#x2019;s top 10 cities (based on MoRTH accident fatality data).</a:t>
            </a:r>
          </a:p>
          <a:p>
            <a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750" algn="ctr">
              <a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/>
              <a:buChar char="•"/>
            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>Economic Benefits: 1 NETRA fleet (8 drones) provides coverage equivalent to 40+ patrol vehicles at ~20% of the operating cost. Faster containment reduces property damage from escalating incidents.</a:t>
            </a:r>
          </a:p>
          <a:p>
            <a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750" algn="ctr">
              <a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/>
              <a:buChar char="•"/>
            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>Environmental: Electric drone fleet produces near-zero emissions vs petrol patrol vehicles. Zero road congestion impact during emergency response &#x2014; drones bypass ground traffic entirely.</a:t>
            </a:r>
          </a:p>
          <a:p>
            <a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750" algn="ctr">
              <a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/>
              <a:buChar char="•"/>
            </a:pPr>
            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>Scale of Problem: India records 2.8M+ road accidents/year (world&#x2019;s highest per MoRTH 2023), 750:1 citizen-to-officer ratio (NCRB), and 16+ min average police response time. NETRA addresses this gap at city scale.</a:t>
            </a:r>
            <a:endParaRPr lang="en-IN" sz="3000" b="1" dirty="0"/>
          </a:p>
